Title: JET Range FVC thermostatic fire valve 95C 10mm 10mtr
Description: Jet FVC Fuelstop safety fire valve designed to shut down the flow of fuel to the appliance in the event of the burner overheating or a fire near the appliance. The valve is to be installed in the oil line at point of entry to the building. The sensor to be passed though the wall into the building and positioned above the burner in accordance with the burner manufacturer's instructions. The oil line and capillary should be sleeved as it passes through walls and there should not be any sharp bends made in the capillary tube. The safety valve is of a robust mechanical design manufactured of non-corrosive materials for external installation. Please ensure that the valve is installed with the reset button pointing down so that rain water cannot enter the valve body. The reset button can be used as an isolation valve when the burner is being serviced by pulling the button down but must be pressed up to activate the valve into the open position before the burner is fired up. Title: Teddington KBB/C/90 fire valve 3mtr
Description: The Teddington KBB/C/90 fire valve is a compact, quick-acting, thermally operated fire safety shut-off valve for use in oil burning equipment. Made of corrosion-resistant, non-combustible materials and entirely mechanical in operation, requiring no power supply, this valve has a non-detachable sensor connected by a capillary and a reset button at the base of the valve head designed to reset the valve or toggle to shut-off condition if pulled. The KBB has a spring-loaded trip mechanism and sealed temperature sensing system made up of bellows, a capillary tube and a sensor phial. Installed in the oil supply pipeline outside a building with the sensor mounted firmly inside the appliance above the burner, the valve simply snaps closed if the temperature at the sensor phial exceeds the set value.
category: Pipe, Valves and Fittings/Metal Pipe Valves/Fire Equipment Accessories/Fire Equipment Accessories.csv -> Teddington KBB/C/90 fire valve 3mtr
